[
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說立世阿毘曇論卷第四",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b06_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "陳西印度三藏真諦譯",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b08_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "14 提頭賴吒城品提頭賴吒城品第十四",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b09_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「須彌山王凡有四頂，東、西、南、北，其東頂者真金所成，其西頂者白銀所成，其北頂者琉璃所成，其南頂者頗梨所成。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b12_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有一切眾寶所成，復多七性。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b13_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是四頂者，上廣下狹，譬如蓮芙，其最狹處周圍一千五百由旬，其最大處逕七百由旬，周圍二千一百由旬。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b15_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是四頂處多有諸獸，復有眾鳥、師子虎豹，並悉化生，一切皆食天須陀味，不相殘害。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b17_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有金剛手，一切諸天依此中住。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b18_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有四由乾陀山：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b18_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一東、二西、三北、四南。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b19_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東由乾陀山，山有兩頂；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b19_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西、北、南亦復如是。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b20_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東二頂者真金所成，西二頂者白銀所成，北二頂者琉璃所成，南二頂者頗梨所成。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復有一切眾寶所成，復有七性。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b22_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "上廣下狹，狀如蓮芙，其最狹處逕三百五十由旬，周圍一千五十由旬，其最大處逕五百由旬，周圍一千五百由旬。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b25_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是八頂處多有諸獸，復有眾鳥、師子虎豹，並悉化生，皆食天須陀味，不相殘害。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "有金剛手，諸天依此中住。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b27_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是山山其頂兩倍，迺至第七尼民陀山，則有五百一十二頂。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190b29_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是七山頂，高廣向外次第半減。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c01_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "東由乾陀山二頂中間，有一國土名提頭賴吒，周圍一千由旬，金城圍遶，高一由旬，埤堄高半由旬，城門高二由旬，門樓一由旬半。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十十由旬有一一門，九十九門復一小門，足一百門。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸門者眾寶所成，摩尼妙寶之所莊嚴，譬如妙好𣰽毺種種雕鏤。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c06_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是門又有四軍防衛，並如上說；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c07_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "外七重寶柵，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c08_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七重多羅樹林之所圍遶，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c08_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其樹中間有諸寶池，相去百弓，種種莊嚴，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c10_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五種寶花，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c10_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及四寶船，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c11_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "池岸五種寶樹，亦如上說，乃至四寶堂殿，諸男女天之所住處。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c12_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其城外邊三重寶塹，餘如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一一塹者廣二由旬，深一由旬半，形如壺口，下廣上狹，天水盈滿，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c14_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是塹間地，有諸婇女宮殿羅列。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三重塹外，七寶樹林之所圍繞，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c16_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時外林中，一切諸花開敷鮮榮，諸女天等奏諸音樂，時諸天子從大城出觀聽音樂，諸女天等從大城出觀聽音樂，以是因緣受諸戲樂。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "提頭賴吒城西南角，是提頭賴吒天王之所住處，周圍二百五十由旬，金城圍遶高一由旬，埤堄高半由旬，城門高二由旬，門樓一由旬半。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十十由旬有一一門，二十四大門復一小門，足二十五門。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸門者眾寶所成，摩尼妙寶之所莊嚴，譬如妙好𣰽毺，種種雕鏤。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c25_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是門又有四軍防衛，並如上說；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "外七重寶柵，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c26_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七重多羅樹林之所圍繞，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c27_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其樹中間有諸寶池，相去百弓，種種莊嚴，亦如上說；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "五種寶花，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c29_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及四寶船，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0190c29_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "池岸五種寶樹，亦如上說，乃至四寶堂殿，諸男女天之所住處。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其城外邊三重寶塹，餘如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "一一塹者廣二由旬，深一由旬半，形如壺口，下廣上狹，天水盈滿，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a04_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是塹間地，有諸婇女宮殿羅列。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a05_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三重塹外，七寶樹林之所圍繞，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a06_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時外林中一切諸花開敷鮮榮，諸女天等奏諸音樂，時諸天子從城中出觀聽音樂，諸女天等從城中出觀聽音樂，以是因緣受諸戲樂。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a09_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是大城內四邊住處、衢巷市鄽並皆調直。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a10_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸天城，或有住處四相應舍、或有住處重層尖屋、或有住處多層高樓、或有住處臺觀雲聳、或有住處四周却敵，隨其福德，眾寶所成，平正端直。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是天城路，其數五十，四陌相通，行列分明，皆如棊道，四門通達，東西相見。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "巷巷市鄽，寶貨盈滿——一穀米市、二衣服市、三眾香市、四飲食市、五花鬘市、六工巧市、七婬女市——處處並有市官。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a17_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸市中，天子天女往來貿易、商量貴賤、求索增減、稱量料數，具市鄽法。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a19_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖作是事，以為戲樂，無取無與、無我所心，脫欲所須，便可提去；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a21_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若業相應，隨意而取；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "業不相應，便作是言：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a22_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『此物奇貴，非我所須。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a22_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』當四衢道，象馬車兵之所莊嚴。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a23_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及諸天子止住其中，或為守護、或為戲樂、或為莊嚴。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a24_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "市中間路，一切琉璃，軟滑可愛，眾寶莊嚴，亦如北地妙好𣰽毺，龍獸花草，皆如前說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "乃至燒香散花、懸諸天衣，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a27_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復於處處竪立幡幢。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "天大城內，如是等聲恒無斷絕，所謂象聲、馬聲、車聲、螺聲、波那婆聲、鼓聲、牟澄伽聲、笳聲、音樂聲。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191a29_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有聲言：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b01_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善來善來。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願食願飲，我今供養。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b01_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是提頭賴吒大城，是天子住處，復有天州、天郡、天縣、天村，周匝遍布此大城中，提頭賴吒天王依此中住。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b04_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王領所極，從由乾陀山東至鐵圍山乾闥婆天，是王所領。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b05_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是義者是佛所說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b06_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "15 毘留勒叉城品毘留勒叉城品第十五「南由乾陀山二頂中間有一國土名毘留勒叉，周圍一千由旬。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b09_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金城圍繞，高一由旬，埤堄高半由旬，城門高二由旬，門樓一由旬半。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十十由旬有一一門，九十九門復一小門，足一百門。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸門者，眾寶所成，摩尼妙寶之所莊嚴，譬如妙好𣰽毺種種雕鏤。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b13_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是門又有四軍防衛，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "外七重寶柵，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "七重多羅樹林之所圍繞，亦如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0191b15_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
