        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有聲言：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a08_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善來善來。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a08_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願食願飲，我今供養。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是毘留勒叉大城，是天子住處，復有天州、天郡、天縣、天村，周匝遍布此大城中。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a10_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "毘樓勒叉天王依此中住。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a11_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王領所極，從由乾陀山南至鐵圍山拘槃荼神，是王所領。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a12_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是義者佛世尊說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a13_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192a13_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
