        "source_sentence": "池岸五種寶樹，乃至四寶堂殿，諸男女天之所住處，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0192c28_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其城外邊有三重寶塹，其一一塹廣二由旬，深一由旬半，形如壺口，下廣上狹，天水盈滿，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是塹間地，有諸婇女堂殿羅列。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a02_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三重塹外，七寶樹林之所圍繞，皆如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a03_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是時外林，一切諸花開敷鮮榮，諸女天等奏諸音樂，時諸天子從大城出觀聽音樂，諸女天等從大城出亦聽音樂，以是因緣受諸戲樂。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a06_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "城西南角，是毘沙門天王之所住處，周圍二百五十由旬。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a08_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "金城圍繞，高一由旬，埤堄高半由旬，城門高二由旬，門樓一由旬半。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a09_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "十十由旬有一一門，二十四大門復一小門，足二十五門。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a11_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸門者眾寶所成，摩尼妙寶之所莊嚴，譬如妙好𣰽毺種種雕鏤。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是門又有四軍防衛。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a13_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "外有七重寶柵，七重寶多羅樹林之所圍繞。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其林中間有諸寶池，相去百弓，種種莊嚴，五種寶花，及四寶船。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "池岸五種寶樹，四寶堂殿，諸男女天之所住處，皆如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "其城外有三重寶塹，其一一塹廣二由旬，深一由旬半，天水盈滿，並如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是塹間地，有諸婇女堂殿羅列。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a19_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "三重塹外，七寶樹林之所圍繞，皆如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a20_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時外林中，一切諸花開敷鮮榮，諸女天等奏諸音樂，時諸天子從城中出，并諸女天並共觀聽，以是因緣受諸戲樂。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a23_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是大城內，四邊住處、衢巷市鄽並皆調直。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a24_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸天城，或有住處四相應舍、或有重層尖屋、或有多層高樓、或有臺觀雲聳、或有四周却敵，隨其福德業，眾寶所成，平正端直。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是天城路其數五十，四陌相通，行列分明，皆如棊道，四門通達，東西相見。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193a28_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "巷巷市鄽寶貨盈滿——一穀米市、二衣服市、三眾香市、四飲食市、五花鬘市、六工巧市、七婬女市——處處並有市官。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b02_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是諸市中天子天女，往來貿易、商量貴賤、求索增減、稱量料數，具市鄽法。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b04_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "雖作此事，以為戲樂，無取無與、無我所心，脫欲所須，便可提去；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b05_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若業相應，隨意而取；",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b06_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "業不相應，便作是言：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b06_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『此物奇貴，非我所須。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b07_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』當四衢道，象馬車兵之所莊嚴。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b07_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "及諸天子止住此處，或為守護、戲樂、莊嚴。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b08_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "市中間路，一切琉璃，軟滑可愛，眾寶莊嚴，亦如北地妙好𣰽毺，龍獸花草，皆如上說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b10_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "燒香散華、懸諸天衣，亦復如是。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b11_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "復於處處竪立幡幢。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b11_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "天大城內，如是等聲恒無斷絕，所謂象、馬、車、螺等聲、波那婆聲、鼓聲、牟澄伽聲、笳聲、音樂聲。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b13_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "又有聲言：",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b14_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "『善來善來。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b14_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "願飲願食，我今供養。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "』是毘沙門大城，是天子住處，復有天洲、天郡、天縣、天村，周匝遍布。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b16_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此大城中，毘沙門天王之所住處。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b17_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "王領所極，從由乾陀北至鐵圍邊一切夜叉神，是王所領。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是毘沙門城，最饒多佉陀尼、蒲闍尼飲食，是故亦名阿羅珂漫陀。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b20_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」如是義者佛世尊說。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是我聞。",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "立世阿毘曇論卷第四",
        "from": "T32n1644_004:0193b21_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]